HEADWORD: Fluviograph
<hw>Flu"vi*o*graph</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>fluvius</ets> river + <ets>-graph</ets>.]</ety> <def>An instrument
